Subject: drm/amdgpu: Move scheduler init to after XGMI is ready
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 5fd8518d187ed03403a4d4f7f56f52c00b11c148
